text.title: UITGEZEILD.
text.p: TEXEL, 17 Sept., Compasrond; Diana, S., Londen. Glenora, Simpson, Newc. - Cort Adler, Larsen, id. - Princess Victoria, Thompsofi, id. - Eider, S., Middlesbro'. - VVoodville, Bright, Engeland. - Houtvaart, Metus, Sundswall. - Omen, Hansen, Frederikstad. - Johannes, Hansen, id. - Judith, Stibolt, Drammen.

VLIE, 16 Sept., N. W.; Niord, Bjornstad, Drobach. HARLINGEN, 17 Sept; Amazonen, Pedersen, Stavanger. - Gjede, Gjertsen, Frederikstad. HELLEVOETSLUIS, 17 Sept., N. O.; Integrity, Hamden, Rye. - Barnest, Modick, Plymouth. - Helen, LaiDg, Newcastle.--3 Zusters, Dijkstra, Stockholm. - Fem Söstre, Knudsen, Tonsberg. — Gisteren nog: Middlesbro', S, Middlesbro' - Edith, S., Huil.

BRIELLE, 17 Sept., N.; Prins van Oranje, S., Duinkerken. - Florence, S., Londen. - Zealous. S., Harwich. BOLDER„, 13 Sept.; Wodan, Meinders, Amst. -Caroline Heymann, Boetius, id. - de Haan, Dekker, id. - Aurora, Vaalman, Leith.
LONDEN, 16 Sept.; de Hoop, Steffens, Petersb. LIVERPOOL, 15 Sept.; Veendam, Potjewijd, Mogador. - Anna Maria Henriette, de Jong, Buenos-Ayros.
